quran[30]{c,v,t}:
  78,1,"en ay shay' yas'al bed kafaar quraysh beda? yatasa'alun ean alkhabar aleazim alshan, wahu alquran aleazim aldhy ynby ean albaeth aldhy shaka fih kafaar quraysh wkdhdhabu bh"
  78,2,"en ay shay' yas'al bed kafaar quraysh beda? yatasa'alun ean alkhabar aleazim alshan, wahu alquran aleazim aldhy ynby ean albaeth aldhy shaka fih kafaar quraysh wkdhdhabu bh"
  78,3,"en ay shay' yas'al bed kafaar quraysh beda? yatasa'alun ean alkhabar aleazim alshan, wahu alquran aleazim aldhy ynby ean albaeth aldhy shaka fih kafaar quraysh wkdhdhabu bh"
  78,4,"ma al'amr kama yazeum hwla' almshrkwn, syelm hwla' almushrikun eaqibat tkdhybhm, wyzhr lahum maa allah faeil bihim yawm alqyamt, thuma sytakd lahum dhlk, wytakd lahum sidq ma ja' bih muhamad salaa allah ealayh wslm, min alquran walbeth. whdha tahdid wweyd lhm"
  78,5,"ma al'amr kama yazeum hwla' almshrkwn, syelm hwla' almushrikun eaqibat tkdhybhm, wyzhr lahum maa allah faeil bihim yawm alqyamt, thuma sytakd lahum dhlk, wytakd lahum sidq ma ja' bih muhamad salaa allah ealayh wslm, min alquran walbeth. whdha tahdid wweyd lhm"
  78,6,alm najeal al'ard mmhdt lakum kalfrash?
  78,7,waljbal rwasy; kay la tataharak bikum alard?
  78,8,wkhlqnakm asnafa dhikrana wantha?
  78,9,"wjelna nawmakum raht labdankm, fih thdwwn wtsknwn?"
  78,10,"wajaealna allayl lbasana talbaskm zlmth wtghshakm, kama ystr althwb labsh?"
  78,11,"wjelna alnahar maeashana tantashirun fih lmeashkm, wtseawn fih lmsalhkm?"
  78,12,"wbnyna fawqakum sabe smwat mtynt albina' mahkamat alkhlq, la sdwe laha wala ftwr?"
  78,13,wjelna alshams srajana wqqadana mdyyana?
  78,14,"wanzlna min alsahb almmtrt ma'an mnsabba bkthrt, linukhrij bih hbana mimaa yqtat bih alnaas whshaysh mimaa takuluh alddawab, wbsatyn mltft bedha bibaed ltsheb aghsanha?"
  78,15,"wanzlna min alsahb almmtrt ma'an mnsabba bkthrt, linukhrij bih hbana mimaa yqtat bih alnaas whshaysh mimaa takuluh alddawab, wbsatyn mltft bedha bibaed ltsheb aghsanha?"
  78,16,"wanzlna min alsahb almmtrt ma'an mnsabba bkthrt, linukhrij bih hbana mimaa yqtat bih alnaas whshaysh mimaa takuluh alddawab, wbsatyn mltft bedha bibaed ltsheb aghsanha?"
  78,17,"'in yawm alfasl bayn alkhlq, wahu yawm alqyamt, kan wqtana wmyeadana mhddana llawlyn walakhryn, yawm yunfakh almalak fi \"alqrn\" 'iydhanana balbeth fatatun ammana, kulu 'umat mae 'imamhm"
  78,18,"'in yawm alfasl bayn alkhlq, wahu yawm alqyamt, kan wqtana wmyeadana mhddana llawlyn walakhryn, yawm yunfakh almalak fi \"alqrn\" 'iydhanana balbeth fatatun ammana, kulu 'umat mae 'imamhm"
  78,19,"wfutht alsma', fakanat dhat 'abwab kathirat lnzwl almlaykt"
  78,20,"wnsft aljibal baed thbwtha, fakanat kalsrab"
  78,21,"'in jahanam kanat yawmayidh trsd 'ahl alkufr aladhin 'ueiddat lhm, lilkafirin mrjeana, maakithin fiha dhwrana mteaqbt la tnqte, la yateamwn fiha ma yubrd hrr alsaeir enhm, wala shrabana yrwyhm, 'iilaa ma'an harana, wsdyd 'ahl alnar, yjazawn bdhlk jaza'an eadla mwafqana laemalhm alty kanuu yemlwnha fi aldnya"
  78,22,"'iina jahanam kanat yawmayidh trsd 'ahl alkufr aladhin 'ueiddat lhm, lilkafirin mrjeana, maakithin fiha dhwrana mteaqbt la tnqte, la yateamwn fiha ma yubrd hrr alsaeir enhm, wala shrabana yrwyhm, 'iilaa ma'an harana, wsdyd 'ahl alnar, yjazawn bdhlk jaza'an eadla mwafqana laemalhm alty kanuu yemlwnha fi aldnya"
  78,23,"'in jahanam kanat yawmayidh trsd 'ahl alkufr aladhin 'ueiddat lhm, lilkafirin mrjeana, maakithin fiha dhwrana mteaqbt la tnqte, la yateamwn fiha ma yubrd hrr alsaeir enhm, wala shrabana yrwyhm, 'iilaa ma'an harana, wsdyd 'ahl alnar, yjazawn bdhlk jaza'an eadla mwafqana laemalhm alty kanuu yemlwnha fi aldnya"
  78,24,"'in jahanam kanat yawmayidh trsd 'ahl alkufr aladhin 'ueiddat lhm, lilkafirin mrjeana, maakithin fiha dhwrana mteaqbt la tnqte, la yateamwn fiha ma yubrd hrr alsaeir enhm, wala shrabana yrwyhm, 'iilaa ma'an harana, wsdyd 'ahl alnar, yjazawn bdhlk jaza'an eadla mwafqana laemalhm alty kanuu yemlwnha fi aldnya"
  78,25,"'in jahanam kanat yawmayidh trsd 'ahl alkufr aladhin 'ueiddat lhm, lilkafirin mrjeana, maakithin fiha dhwrana mteaqbt la tnqte, la yateamwn fiha ma yubrd hrr alsaeir enhm, wala shrabana yrwyhm, 'iilaa ma'an harana, wsdyd 'ahl alnar, yjazawn bdhlk jaza'an eadla mwafqana laemalhm alty kanuu yemlwnha fi aldnya"
  78,26,"'in jahanam kanat yawmayidh trsd 'ahl alkufr aladhin 'ueiddat lhm, lilkafirin mrjeana, maakithin fiha dhwrana mteaqbt la tnqte, la yateamwn fiha ma yubrd hrr alsaeir enhm, wala shrabana yrwyhm, 'iilaa ma'an harana, wsdyd 'ahl alnar, yjazawn bdhlk jaza'an eadla mwafqana laemalhm alty kanuu yemlwnha fi aldnya"
  78,27,"'iinahum kanuu la yakhafun yawm alhisab falam yaemaluu lh, wkdhdhabu bima ja'athum bih alrusul tkdhyba, wkll shay' ealamnah wktbnah fi allwh almhfwz, fadhuquu -ayha alkafrwn- jaza'an aemalkm, falan nazidakum 'iilaa edhabana fawq edhabkm"
  78,28,"'inhm kanuu la yakhafun yawm alhisab falam yaemaluu lh, wkdhdhabu bima ja'athum bih alrusul tkdhyba, wkll shay' ealamnah wktbnah fi allwh almhfwz, fadhuquu -ayha alkafrwn- jaza'an aemalkm, falan nazidakum 'iilaa edhabana fawq edhabkm"
  78,29,"'inhm kanuu la yakhafun yawm alhisab falam yaemaluu lh, wkdhdhabu bima ja'athum bih alrusul tkdhyba, wkll shay' ealamnah wktbnah fi allwh almhfwz, fadhuquu -ayha alkafrwn- jaza'an aemalkm, falan nazidakum 'iilaa edhabana fawq edhabkm"
  78,30,"'inhm kanuu la yakhafun yawm alhisab falam yaemaluu lh, wkdhdhabu bima ja'athum bih alrusul tkdhyba, wkll shay' ealamnah wktbnah fi allwh almhfwz, fadhuquu -ayha alkafrwn- jaza'an aemalkm, falan nazidakum 'iilaa edhabana fawq edhabkm"